&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;airly2000 &lt;airly2002@...&gt;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt; wrote:&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE style=&quot;PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px; BORDER-LEFT: #1010ff 2px solid&quot;&gt;&lt;TT&gt;Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Elita yawed and left fall the bottle. She was tired but she didn&#39;t &lt;BR&gt;like rest inside her crib.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Rodimus watched as his daughter drank the energon.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Rodimus Prime: There you go, little one. Learn to use your robot &lt;BR&gt;mode parts.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; airly2000 &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Elita &quot;caught&quot; the bottle but she couldn&#39;t set it in her mounth, &lt;BR&gt;she &lt;BR&gt;&gt; hadn&#39;t enoguh coordination with her hands until she did it. Elita &lt;BR&gt;&gt; started to suck the energon.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus allowed Elita to catch the bottle so she could drink the &lt;BR&gt;&gt; energon.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Oh, you got it. Drink up, hunny.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; airly2000 &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Elita moved her little arms trying to get the bottle, she was &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; giggling aloud. IT was such fun!!!!&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; -- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus carries Elita with him as he gets her bottle. He waves &lt;BR&gt;&gt; it &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; around in front of her.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Get the food! Elita has to get the food!&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000 &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Elita attempted to catch one of Daddy&#39;s hadns. Soon she&#39;d feel &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; hungry and tired, but she liked to play a while more with her &lt;BR&gt;&gt; dad.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, &quot;Nic&quot; &lt;Proudwing500k@h...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Yggdrasil: We&#39;re still discussing details, but I&#39;ll report &lt;BR&gt;&gt; back &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; very&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; soon. Prime out.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; He frowned in a way that was very similar as that of his &lt;BR&gt;&gt; infamous&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Autobot ancestor. Kup&#39;s team was good, but it exposed them &lt;BR&gt;too &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; much,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; he thought.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Yggdrasil: I don&#39;t like the idea that all three highest &lt;BR&gt;&gt; officers &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; here,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; meaning you, Rodimus and me, get to go. It will be a &lt;BR&gt;drawback &lt;BR&gt;&gt; if &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; the&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; preds decide to move out just then. I suggest that Rodimus &lt;BR&gt;&gt; stays &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; and&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that we replace him with either Empath or Blackfang, or even &lt;BR&gt;&gt; one &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; of&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; the new guys around.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus holds her close, tickling her, while he takes care &lt;BR&gt;&gt; of &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; business.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; He opens a comm.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Yggdrasil, what&#39;s the status of that team?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Airshadow Nightstar &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita continued giggling and laughting. She was enjoying a &lt;BR&gt;&gt; lot&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; playing with her daddy. She was having a lot fun and if she &lt;BR&gt;&gt; would &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; be a&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; little older, she would have wished that it never ends.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To: &lt;BR&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 May 2003 21:59:17 -0700 &lt;BR&gt;&gt; (PDT) &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus was having fun playing with his &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; daughter,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; but his thoughts started to dwell on Nightlight. He wished &lt;BR&gt;she &lt;BR&gt;&gt; was&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; there so they could all be together as a family. &gt; &gt;Rodimus &lt;BR&gt;&gt; tossed&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita up just a little bit, then cought her. &gt; &gt; &gt;Airshadow &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Nightstar&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt;Elita: &gt; &gt;Elita Laughtes Aloud, that was such fun. &lt;BR&gt;She &lt;BR&gt;&gt; was&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; gigglig pleaced while she spread her little arms toward her &lt;BR&gt;&gt; dad &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;From: Richard Allen &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &lt;BR&gt;&gt;To:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 &lt;BR&gt;May &lt;BR&gt;&gt; 2003&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; 21:27:31 -0700 (PDT) &gt; &gt;: : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus looks &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; stunned&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; after getting hit in the nose. &gt; &gt;Rodimus Prime: I got your &lt;BR&gt;&gt; hand, &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; but&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; you got daddy&#39;s nose. &gt; &gt;Rodimus raises her over his head &lt;BR&gt;and &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; spins&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; around twice. &gt; &gt; &gt;airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt;Elita laughted &lt;BR&gt;&gt; more &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; and&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; without liked with her jerking movement she &gt;struck slighty &lt;BR&gt;her&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; daddy&#39;s nose &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Allen&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;wrote: &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; Rodimus traps two of &lt;BR&gt;her &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; fingers&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; in his mouth, playing around. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: I got &lt;BR&gt;&gt; your &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; hand,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; what&#39;cha gunna do? &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Elita&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; giggled a lot, she touched with one of her little hand his &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; daddy&#39;s&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; chin. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Richard&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Allen &gt;wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus &lt;BR&gt;picks &lt;BR&gt;&gt; up &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; his&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; daughter, holding her close. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: I &lt;BR&gt;can &lt;BR&gt;&gt; tell&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that you are going to be a strong girl. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; airly2000&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Eliata laughted and giggled more &lt;BR&gt;she &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; spread&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; her little arms &gt;towards &gt; &gt; &gt; her daddy. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; -&lt;BR&gt;--&lt;BR&gt;&gt; In&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : : &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus looked at his fully transformed &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; daughter. He&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; could see &gt; &gt; the &gt; &gt; &gt; influences from Nightlight and &lt;BR&gt;&gt; himself. &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Now you see your true form hunny. &lt;BR&gt;You &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; are &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; a &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; cybertroian transformer. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;airly2000&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita started to laught more &lt;BR&gt;and &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; more.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Sometimes, by seconds, &gt; &gt; &gt; seemed &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that her little &lt;BR&gt;&gt; chest&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; would open to show the rest of her robot &gt; &gt; &gt; mode. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; At &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; last,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that help her to complete her tranform. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; She &lt;BR&gt;&gt; looked&lt